@S_ms wrote:

Welcome!

okay, this isn't in the right forum, but i'll help you. It's kinda easy: you have a client. Make a new dir in the same directory as your client, and call it cache. Now go to %windir% and copy .file_store_32 into the cache folder, so you will have [serverclient folder]\cache.file_store_32\ [all rs data]

Now it should work
